.SH NAME
ripcd \- ripcd v0.0.0
.sp
Rip audio CD to FLAC with CDDB metadata. Linux only. Requires \fBcdparanoia\fP and \fBflac\fP in PATH.
.SH COMMANDS
.SS ripcd
.sp
Rip an audio disc to FLAC files.
.sp
Requires cdparanoia and flac to be in PATH.
.sp
For Linux only.
.sp
